if you want to update the lib, the following content can be FYI.

1,get the zip file from http://code.google.com/p/googletest/downloads/list
2,put the zip file to your DIR
3,unzip zip file
4,install according to README
	./configure --prefix=$YOUR_INSTALL_PATH
	make
	cd make 
	make
5,copy $DIR/include $DIR/make/gtest_main.a to $YOUR_INSTALL_PATH, and you'd better rename gtest_main.a to gtest.a
6,update current dir with the include and libgtest.a 
